snippet.title: Armed and Gelatinous: Couch Edition | Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
After years of eating quarters in arcades across the country, Armed and Gelatinous: Couch Edition is the new and improved console version of the arcade party game to end all party games!

Features
- Keep the party going with 9 Unique Game Modes
- Become Unblobable with 16 Lethal Weapons
- Dash across the galaxy in 16 Different Levels
- Challenge friends or take on AI opponents with 5 CPU Difficulty Levels

Armed and Gelatinous: Couch Edition will be available on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 5|4, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, and Steam on May 2, 2024!

Mark your calendar and warm up those couch cushions!

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/446510
Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/blobsonline
Official Website: https://armedandgelatinous.com

Music:
Zac Zinger - Swingin' at the Speed of Light
Armed and Gelatinous OST
